<h2>How we work </h2>

<div class="image-float">
    <a href="https://www.thelancet.com/journals/lancet/article/PIIS0140-6736(17)32443-1/fulltext?code=lancet-site"><img src="/images/lancet-100millionlives.jpg" alt="Lancet: Saving an additional 100 million lives"></a>
